The Heart of the Game;;83;;87;;PG-13;;Filmed over a period of seven years, director Ward Serrill profiles Bill Resler, a university professor who coaches a basketball team comprised of high-school girls. Darnellia Russell, one of the team's few black players, also comes into focus as she struggles to stay on the team despite major obstacles.;;Documentary;;Ward Serrill;;2005;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-heart-of-the-game